FuncDef: This command displays WLAN-GW group information, including WLAN-GW tunnels.

ParaDef.Info: Displays information about the specified WLAN-GW group ID. Values-1 to 4.
Displays information about associations for the specified WLAN-GW group ID.
Displays information about the WLAN-GW-specific status and basic statistics information about the specified member. Values-1 to 255.

Displays a reduced output to only show statistics of the specified type. Values-packet-errors, host-errors, bd-errors, forwarding,                   reassembly, aa, radius, arp, dhcp, dhcp6, icmp, icmp6.
Displays a reduced output to only show statistics whose value is bigger than zero.
Displays the resource usage on the specified group member.
Displays statistics information about the members of the specified WLAN-GW group.
